thread.title: BRIEF-National Fuel Q1 Earnings Per Share $2.30

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-National Fuel Q1 Earnings Per Share $2.30
text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - National Fuel Gas Co:
* NATIONAL FUEL REPORTS FIRST QUARTER EARNINGS * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $2.30 * SEES FY 2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE $3.20 TO $3.40 * QUARTERLY ADJUSTED OPERATING RESULTS PER SHARE $1.02 * SEES FY 2018 CONSOLIDATED CAPITAL EXPENDITURES IN RANGE OF $560 MILLION - $650 MILLION
* QUARTERLY NET NATURAL GAS AND OIL PRODUCTION OF 40.1 BCFE
* SEES FY 2018 TOTAL PRODUCTION 180 TO 195 BCFE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
